timing_socv_p...th_annotations(25.10)    timing_socv_p...th_annotations(25.10)

Name
       timing_socv_preserve_variation_with_annotations

Syntax
       timing_socv_preserve_variation_with_annotations

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Preserves  the sigma value computed by delay calculation along with the
       annotation from SDC.

       In the clock mesh flow, it is possible to preserve  sigma  values  even
       after applying annotation on slew/delay through SDC.

       When  this  global  variable  is  set to true, the software accepts the
       sigma value computed by delay  calculation  (for  nets  that  have  de-
       lay/slew  annotations from SDC, e.g., clock-mesh), along with the anno-
       tation from SDC.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

